    PolicyLoader --> PolicyVersion : stores history
    PolicyLoader --> RedisCache : reads/writes policy cache
    PolicyLoader --> OPAEvaluator : loads active policy
    PolicyLoader --> NorviqError : raises on rollback miss
    PolicyLoader --> NorviqSettings : settings import
    F011 --> PolicyLoader : startup load()
    F015 --> PolicyLoader : startup/reload
    F016 --> PolicyLoader : webhook reload()
    F017 --> PolicyLoader : create()/rollback()
    F022 --> PolicyLoader : CRD event source

